[b][u][size=12pt]CURRENTLY THERE ARE 2 POSITIONS OPEN[/size][/u][/b] This will be about the development of Android 634
This server will require a lot of work since it is an almost blank base. Also you will knowledge of 614 server coding. As it is based on the 614 revision.
[u][b][/b][/u]
